        <li><a href="https://artychan.makes.org/thimble/keep-calm-and/remix">Keep Calm Poster</a> (<a href="https://artychan.makes.org/thimble/keep-calm-poster-tutorial/remix">tutorial</a>)</li>
        <li><a href="https://thimble.webmaker.org/project/22957/remix">Rainy Day (<a href="https://artychan.makes.org/thimble/rainy-day-tutorial">tutorial</a>)</a></li>
